President Muhammadu Buhari, on Wednesday, visited the correctional centre in Kuje in the federal capital territory (FCT). The correctional facility was attacked on Tuesday night by gunmen using explosives. Buhari was on the ground to assess the extent of the damage caused. See pictures below. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-721153" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-721152" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-3-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-721151" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Buharis-visit-to-Kuje-prison-2.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" s